description: RMF layout element <defaults> to set page-wide defaults (borders, tooltips)
---

### Options
- `noborder` — turn off borders for following areas.
- `border <width> <lineWidth> <colour>` — default border for following areas.
- `tiptint <colour>` — tooltip text colour.
- `tipbtint <colour>` — tooltip background colour.
- `tipfont <font>` — tooltip font.

